Package com.openfeint.api

Class Summary
Notification All Notifications (popups that give the user information) in OpenFeint derive from this class.
Notification.Delegate This class provides the basic behavior for filtering and displaying notifications.
OpenFeint Shared entry point for initializing OpenFeint and getting access to its current state.
OpenFeintDelegate Callback class that you provide to OpenFeint.initialize() to get notified of OpenFeint-related events.
OpenFeintSettings Object exposing all available application settings for use during OpenFeint initialization.
 

Enum Summary
Notification.Category The Category enum describes what category a Notification belongs to.
Notification.Type The Type enum describes what type of Notification this is.
